trans-unit.source: The general practitioners of the medical center offer curative follow-up but also attach great importance to the preventive aspect.
trans-unit.target: The general practitioners of the medical center offer curative follow-up but also attach great importance to the preventive aspect.

A series of treatments are organized there, for example: blood tests, wound care, drug injections, syringing of earwax plugs, blood pressure monitoring, occasional vaccines outside of vaccination campaigns for which another permanence is organized as well as home visits for patients who cannot come to the dispensary.

trans-unit.source: Our social worker guides and helps patients in difficulty with medico-social and administrative procedures relating to their health.
